item.title: CVE-2022-31591|2024-08-03T07:19:06.822Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20businessobjects%20%28bw%20publisher%20service%29
item.description: SAP BusinessObjects BW Publisher Service - versions 420, 430, uses a search path that contains an unquoted element. A local attacker can gain elevated privileges by inserting an executable file in the path of the affected service
